### **Day 4 – Binary Search on Answers (Part 2)**

1. [LeetCode 378 – Kth Smallest Element in a Sorted Matrix](https://leetcode.com/problems/kth-smallest-element-in-a-sorted-matrix/)
2. [LeetCode 668 – Kth Smallest Number in Multiplication Table](https://leetcode.com/problems/kth-smallest-number-in-multiplication-table/)
