5. (Optional repeat) [LeetCode 875 – Koko Eating Bananas](https://leetcode.com/problems/koko-eating-bananas/) – redo to solidify.

---

### **Day 5 – Matrix & 2D Binary Search**

1. [LeetCode 74 – Search a 2D Matrix](https://leetcode.com/problems/search-a-2d-matrix/)
2. [LeetCode 240 – Search a 2D Matrix II](https://leetcode.com/problems/search-a-2d-matrix-ii/)
3. [LeetCode 378 – Kth Smallest Element in a Sorted Matrix](https://leetcode.com/problems/kth-smallest-element-in-a-sorted-matrix/) – revisit with optimized approach.
4. [GFG – Median in Row-Wise Sorted Matrix](https://practice.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/median-in-a-row-wise-sorted-matrix1527/1)
5. Variation practice: do LC 240 again with binary search per row.

---

### **Day 6 – Advanced / Hard**

1. [LeetCode 4 – Median of Two Sorted Arrays](https://leetcode.com/problems/median-of-two-sorted-arrays/)
2. [LeetCode 2141 – Maximum Running Time of N Computers](https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-running-time-of-n-computers/)
3. [LeetCode 1231 – Divide Chocolate](https://leetcode.com/problems/divide-chocolate/)
