5. [LeetCode 302 – Smallest Rectangle Enclosing Black Pixels](https://leetcode.com/problems/smallest-rectangle-enclosing-black-pixels/)

---

### **Day 7 – God Stage Review + Mock Drill**

- Pick 3–5 random problems from above, mix basics + hard (e.g., LC 33, LC 875, LC 4, LC 2141).
- Solve under **timed conditions** (30–40 min each).
- Re-write clean **binary search templates** for:

  - Classic 1D array
  - Lower/upper bound
  - Rotated array
  - Binary search on answer
  - 2D matrix
